<div class='spoiler'>
This answer contains spoilers…
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    No, that is their first meeting, even though the book mentions that Deeti foresaw their meeting and Zachary will later be added to her shrine. Their m<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    No, that is their first meeting, even though the book mentions that Deeti foresaw their meeting and Zachary will later be added to her shrine. Their meeting is significant because it is their first meeting and they are arguably the two most prominent characters in the book.<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
 <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
